\slidetitle{Overview of xplan}
\begin{topitemize}

\item xplan is a tool used for project scheduling.

\item The motivation for xplan is to provide a pictorial or tabular
representation of tasks that must be accomplished from beginning to
end of a project. 

\item Components include:
	\begin{itemize}
	\item User Interface
	\item Database
	\item File Read / Write 
        \item Calculations
        \item Latex Generator
	\end{itemize}
\item Future extensions include:
	\begin{itemize}
	\item Allow subtasks within a given task
	\item Allow for more than one project at a time within the program
	\item Uses as a management tool (via.\ costs of resources)
	\end{itemize}
\end{topitemize}
